dialogue: Danger! A magazine has been discovered in marketing!
Gather the other engineers. We must get that magazine.
We think it was a careless mistake by someone in the mail department.
As you know, there is nothing more dangerous than a marketing person with a little bit of knowledge.
We know where the magazine will be read. We need nets, rope and tranquilizer darts.
I'll have to ask engineering to build one of these space stations...
